Napoleon's travel Q™ 285X has everything you need for perfect portable grilling anywhere. Featuring all-terrain wheels, easy folding, setup, and compact storage. Two burners provide precise heat for indirect grilling and smoking, or high heat searing and is ideal for cooking small chickens or roasts thanks to a high-top cast aluminum lid.
